316
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:32,180
It's always good to visit New York again after a long time, huh?

317
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,580
I ain't visiting here "after a long time"!

318
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:39,780
It's ok, but let's just hurry up on the eraser.

319
00:13:40,180 --> 00:13:42,180
Ah, that won't be any good.

320
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,780
Have you done any shopping here?

321
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:44,780
Shopping?!

322
00:13:44,780 --> 00:13:48,980
Of course not! I'm on a mission here! I didn't even get any souvenir.

323
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:52,180
No problem! Let's just go shopping!

324
00:13:52,780 --> 00:13:54,180
Why the hell should we?

