00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:23,780
And the Batsu Game is finally reaching its climax!

334
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:25,180
How is this also part of the Batsu Game?

335
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:26,780
Since you lost that bet, can't be helped.

336
00:14:26,780 --> 00:14:29,580
Why must I do this again? That's what's annoying to me.

337
00:14:30,780 --> 00:14:32,380
Can't be helped.

338
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:34,380
It's cold here!

339
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:40,580
Another reunion with Sakamoto Ryuichi after 38 hours!

340
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:51,180
I'm exhausted...

341
00:14:52,380 --> 00:14:52,980
Ah, Kyoju!

342
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:55,180
The eraser?

343
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:59,380
You're late...

344
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:02,500
What do you mean we're late?

345
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:03,500
