346
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,180
Sakamoto!

347
00:15:06,300 --> 00:15:06,900
Is this it?

348
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:09,580
Ah, yes. Sorry. That's what I came for.

349
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:17,300
Through Kyoju's hand, the eraser is warmly handed, describing parabola.

350
00:15:12,780 --> 00:15:18,580
Eraser fetching success!!

351
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,780
The Batsu Game is complete!

352
00:15:22,100 --> 00:15:24,300
It's so irritating...

353
00:15:24,780 --> 00:15:26,780
Let's go, you already got the eraser...

354
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,780
That's how Grammy Awards change a man, huh?

355
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:29,780
Alright then!

356
00:15:29,780 --> 00:15:31,380
I'll start making music tomorrow!

357
00:15:33,380 --> 00:15:36,380
I'm gonna challenge you! I'm gonna make music...

358
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:38,580
I'll meet you again at the next Grammy Award ceremony!

359
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:40,580
Farewell!!

360
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:45,780
Eraser's fetched. Hamada is off from New York once again!

361
00:15:42,980 --> 00:15:45,780
And now, to Japan where Matsumoto awaits!

362
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:51,180
Right?

363
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:53,580
Board room

