00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:58,780
78 hours since the first departure

366
00:15:58,980 --> 00:15:59,580
Is this it!?

367
00:15:59,980 --> 00:16:01,780
Yeah! This is the one...

368
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:05,180
Y'know...you should've checked for this eraser the first time.

369
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:07,580
Now it's finally complete.

370
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:12,380
Oh, I want Evian water too.

371
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:13,980
Here you go then.

372
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:15,780
No, not this one.

373
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:17,980
Why not?

374
00:16:21,180 --> 00:16:23,180
Go over there.

375
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:28,180
Go draw some Evian water in France.

376
00:16:28,900 --> 00:16:29,980
Gimme a break already!

377
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:40,100
You should have gone to France.

378
00:16:40,100 --> 00:16:41,300
WHY!?

379
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:43,380
Considering audience's reaction, it's so!

380
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,580
Oh they are like "Oh he goes to France now?"...

381
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:46,780
Right?

382
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:49,180
Still, going to New York was really exhausting...

383
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:50,700
I've heard that was tiring.

384
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:52,180
Yeah, VERY TIRING!

385
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,980
Moreover, you didn't have any sleep, right?

386
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,380
Yeah, I just had to go back in a day!

387
00:16:55,380 --> 00:16:59,580
Well, you had to go through that because I experienced similar things.

388
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:00,780
What's that?

389
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:02,780
What similar thing?

390
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:05,380
The next Batsu Game is already decided.

391
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:06,180
Oh, really?

392
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:07,580
What is it?

393
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:08,980
Um...

394
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:10,180
You go to the North Pole...

395
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:14,380
...and become Coolmint gum.

396
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:17,780
Penguin?

397
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:19,580
Note: Reference from advertising from Coolmint gum, Lotte.

398
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:22,180
I'm gonna sell that from Lotte.

399
00:17:24,180 --> 00:17:25,780
Like some kind of limited products.

400
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:26,900
Well, well...

401
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:31,900
When I was in the plane, there was a couple behind me.

402
00:17:32,380 --> 00:17:36,380
Then, the girl said to me "Can I have your autograph?".

403
00:17:36,580 --> 00:17:39,580
I said it's ok. I have nothing to do after all.

404
00:17:39,580 --> 00:17:43,580
She said, "I'm gonna take my clothes off". I was like, "Huh!?".

405
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:49,980
She hand me her bra and said, "Sign to this".

406
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:52,580
It's totally insane!

407
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:54,380
It was so warm!

408
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:59,180
I signed that warm bra...

409
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,580
Don't smell it man, don't smell it...

410
00:18:04,980 --> 00:18:09,780
Also, I didn't eat anything on the plane home. Because I was too tired.

411
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:10,780
No appetite.

412
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:12,300
I didn't give a shit about food in the plane.

413
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:13,380
I just wanted to sleep!

414
00:18:13,980 --> 00:18:17,780
When I was sleeping all the way, about 5 hours left,

415
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:21,180
A foreigner cabin attendant who spoke Japanese very well came to me and said-

416
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:25,380
"You didn't eat anything, right?". Then, I responded "Yeah.".

417
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:30,780
"If you go back from foreign country and didn't eat anything-

418
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:33,380
you'll be mistaken as a drug mule."

419
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:38,180
Right, right...

420
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:41,780
She said drug mules often don't eat anything and just go out!

421
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:45,780
If they eat anything, drugs will go wrong.

422
00:18:46,380 --> 00:18:49,780
So they wrap drugs into plastic bag or something and swallow it-

423
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:52,180
then they bring it to Japan.

424
00:18:52,180 --> 00:18:55,380
Since I haven't eaten anything, and just kept sleeping...

425
00:18:55,380 --> 00:19:01,980
Other foreign attendants kept looking at me when they pass by.

426
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:06,780
She said "You are not a drug mule, aren't you?", I was like "Hell no!"

427
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:09,780
Well, but...you were carrying drugs...

